{"id": 2934, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得啥样的人才算「会玩」？", "description": "一个人的高「玩商」都具体体现在哪儿？", "record_count": 2884, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190506103855NueKF9lDf73bR46X.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-08T03:00:28Z", "options": [{"id": 342791, "content": "去景区，知道怎么避开人多的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 342792, "content": "拍照的时候知道怎么凹不那么游客照的造型", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 343048, "content": "没钱能玩的开心才是真的会玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 667, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 343049, "content": "知道苍蝇馆子也了解米其林，了解热门景点里的小路，也知道小众景点的玩法。\n晚上两个人在家，如何把时间变得更有趣。 一个人，如何逗自己开心。", "image": "img/option/option/201905081112435sgJEf3znmShjX7l.png", "praise_count": 517, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738382}, {"id": 343050, "content": "玩什么东西都可以吸引别人也去玩一下。哪怕是💩", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650188}, {"id": 342795, "content": "对啥都有兴趣，出门玩的时候会注意到很细节的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 347, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 343051, "content": "一个人的生活也过的丰富多彩很充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 176, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648592}, {"id": 343052, "content": "真实又跳脱  纠结体", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317470}, {"id": 343053, "content": "音乐节上五六十岁的大妈们，像是春游一样坐在草地上开心的玩耍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 343054, "content": "学霸，但是平时有经常玩游戏，玩得很溜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 343055, "content": "开心就好，毫无束缚", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 343056, "content": "持续的好奇心与持续的探究。", "image": null, "praise_count": 258, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445140}, {"id": 343568, "content": "脾气不好性子傲，吊儿郎当又爱笑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1651513}, {"id": 343057, "content": "低成本，大乐趣，敢于挑战有冒险精神不玩命老少皆宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650207}, {"id": 343059, "content": "随风而行，随遇而安", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 343060, "content": "不管玩什么都能全情投入，不抱怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 218, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647797}, {"id": 343063, "content": "于谦于老师。玩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649787}, {"id": 343319, "content": "有底气的选择最适合的选项。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 343064, "content": "有钱人就会玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620968}, {"id": 343321, "content": "能让所有人都有参与感并玩得开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264344}, {"id": 343067, "content": "一个人独处也不会觉得孤独。敢于尝试和懂得发现生活中不经意的美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 154, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861604}, {"id": 343068, "content": "玩的东西让别人看后会觉得自己学不会的既视感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926806}, {"id": 343069, "content": "借钱吃好的，不算不会过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 343070, "content": "反正别看小红书就是了", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681648}, {"id": 343071, "content": "善于从平凡的生活中寻找乐趣 或 拥有一双好奇的眼睛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439993}, {"id": 343072, "content": "会有很多随性而为", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309481}, {"id": 343073, "content": "91大神", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465689}, {"id": 343075, "content": "把工作和生活分开，每一分钟生活到可以是玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697539}, {"id": 343587, "content": "会“投胎”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625789}, {"id": 343076, "content": "自娱自乐的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143431}, {"id": 344356, "content": "在大部分活动中，都想创造不一样的内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1653844}, {"id": 343077, "content": "无聊也很有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075634}, {"id": 343078, "content": "把日常生活过出新的含义", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 45594}, {"id": 343079, "content": "尽兴", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276287}, {"id": 343080, "content": "是我啊哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499926}, {"id": 343081, "content": "既能寄情山水也能大隐于市", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634944}, {"id": 343082, "content": "会不会玩我不懂了，一天到晚就知道傻乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256841}, {"id": 343083, "content": "调剂得了一个人的生活，也喜欢钻进人群，但还是自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 343085, "content": "沙雕", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650274}, {"id": 343086, "content": "能让自己开心的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1608153}, {"id": 343087, "content": "不介意他人的目光，专注于自己的嗜好，满足自己。", "image": "img/option/option/20190508153824sqe1QbNTgkWM4i9X.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593883}, {"id": 343088, "content": "能在常见的生活中发现别人看不到的点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100708}, {"id": 343089, "content": "能在常见的生活中发现别人看不到的点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100708}, {"id": 343090, "content": "自由自在，无拘无束，解放天性", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650326}, {"id": 343602, "content": "从每次玩的新东西里，都能get到新技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265413}, {"id": 343091, "content": "敢于尝试", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631031}, {"id": 343092, "content": "会因为各种各样的事情开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650333}, {"id": 344372, "content": "懂得自律 也享受自由的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654133}, {"id": 343093, "content": "一个人也能过得很充足，善于发现身边有趣的小事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453201}, {"id": 343095, "content": "不刻意，但会让我捧腹。哈哈，这人就是我的老公", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585058}]}